  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Which are the best news app for an android phone?",
  "response": "There are several excellent news apps available for Android phones. Here are some of the best options:\n\n1. **Google News**\n   - **Features**: Personalized news feed based on your interests, access to a wide range of news sources, and a clean, user-friendly interface.\n   - **Pros**: Highly customizable, integrates well with other Google services, and provides full coverage of breaking news.\n\n2. **Flipboard**\n   - **Features**: A magazine-style layout that lets you flip through articles, the ability to create your own custom magazines, and a vast selection of topics.\n   - **Pros**: Visually appealing, great for discovering new content, and offers a social aspect where you can follow and share with others.\n\n3. **BBC News**\n   - **Features**: Comprehensive coverage of global news, live streaming of BBC channels, and in-depth analysis on various topics.\n   - **Pros**: Reliable and trusted source of news, easy navigation, and useful notifications for breaking news.\n\n4. **Reuters**\n   - **Features**: Focused on business and financial news, real-time market data, and global coverage with a reputation for accuracy.\n   - **Pros**: Ideal for those interested in finance and business, fast updates, and an ad-free experience with the premium version.\n\n5. **Feedly**\n   - **Features**: Aggregates news from your favorite sources into one place, supports RSS feeds, and allows you to organize articles into boards.\n   - **Pros**: Highly customizable, great for power users who want to curate their own news sources, and integrates well with other productivity apps.\n\n6. **AP News**\n   - **Features**: Covers breaking news, politics, sports, and more, with personalized news alerts and a straightforward interface.\n   - **Pros**: Reliable source, easy to use, and provides comprehensive coverage of U.S. and global news.\n\n7. **Microsoft Start (formerly Microsoft News)**\n   - **Features**: Curated news feed, integration with other Microsoft services, and personalized content based on your interests.\n   - **Pros**: Diverse range of news sources, user-friendly design, and additional features like weather updates and stock information.\n\nEach of these apps has its own strengths, so the best choice for you will depend on your specific needs and preferences. You might want to try out a few to see which one suits you best.",
